data.description: Nestled on a spacious .64-acre lot, this inviting home is a haven of tranquility. The three well-appointed bedrooms include a primary bedroom with convenient access to the full main bathroom.  Step into culinary excellence in the large kitchen, adorned with beautiful granite countertops. Equipped with modern appliances, this space becomes the heart of the home, perfect for both entertaining and daily living.  The living spaces are open and bathed in natural light, creating a welcoming atmosphere that complements the tasteful finishes throughout.   The basement of this property underwent significant improvements in 2016, including the reinforcement of the walls and a comprehensive waterproofing process. These enhancements ensure a secure and dry environment, providing peace of mind to the future homeowner.   Outside, the expansive backyard is a true retreat, offering endless possibilities for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply taking in the fresh air. The large lot size ensures privacy, making it an ideal haven.  Beat the rush of the spring market by making an offer now. Schedule a showing today and envision the warm and inviting lifestyle that awaits at 12965 C St., LaSalle, MI. Begin your journey to a new chapter and a fresh start in a home designed for comfort and celebration.
